1
00:00:06,042 --> 00:00:08,467
♫ I want to go to the future ♫

2
00:00:08,467 --> 00:00:12,122
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,122 --> 00:00:18,315
♫  I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head  ♫

4
00:00:18,315 --> 00:00:24,441
♫  I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

5
00:00:24,441 --> 00:00:30,662
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:30,662 --> 00:00:35,948
♫  We are always looking forward to the unknown future  ♫

7
00:00:35,948 --> 00:00:43,148
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,148 --> 00:00:48,272
♫ Every day my heart beats for you ♫

9
00:00:48,272 --> 00:00:49,885
♫  Be your light  ♫

10
00:00:49,885 --> 00:00:55,648
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,648 --> 00:01:02,048
♫  Every day the sun shines through the window  ♫

12
00:01:02,048 --> 00:01:08,715
♫  With your reflection being my incredible highlight  ♫

13
00:01:08,715 --> 00:01:11,702
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:16,690 --> 00:01:19,460
I wonder how the wedding is going.

15
00:01:22,580 --> 00:01:25,480
Do they have a lot of delicious food at a wedding?

16
00:01:25,480 --> 00:01:29,540
That's not true. The dishes at weddings are the worst.

17
00:01:35,580 --> 00:01:38,139
Beibei, why are you upset?

18
00:01:38,139 --> 00:01:40,580
It's not Gao Yang's wedding.

19
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:47,067
We said the three of us will go to the wedding together and they didn't bring me along.

20
00:01:47,067 --> 00:01:49,359
Who did he end up bringing?

21
00:01:49,359 --> 00:01:50,940
Xiaowen.

22
00:01:50,940 --> 00:01:52,636
Isn't that absurd?

23
00:01:54,740 --> 00:01:57,619
He said the three of them are family.

24
00:01:57,619 --> 00:01:59,019
They can't be separated.

25
00:01:59,019 --> 00:02:00,859
Is Gao Yang's step-father an outstanding man?

26
00:02:00,859 --> 00:02:02,819
What kind of person is he?

27
00:02:04,100 --> 00:02:07,779
He's richer than Uncle Gao and younger than Uncle Gao.

28
00:02:08,260 --> 00:02:11,339
Well, a lot of people are like that.

29
00:02:11,339 --> 00:02:13,203
So shallow!

30
00:02:20,260 --> 00:02:21,900
Dawei.

31
00:02:21,900 --> 00:02:23,880
Why are you guys here? Where's Gao Yang?

32
00:02:23,880 --> 00:02:26,419
Gao Yang went to his mother's wedding.
(T/N: "his mother" can be used as a swear in Chinese)

33
00:02:26,419 --> 00:02:30,299
No, no, I'm not cursing at you. I said he went to his mom's wedding.

34
00:02:30,299 --> 00:02:31,940
Come eat with us.

35
00:02:31,940 --> 00:02:33,840
I'm good. You guys enjoy.

36
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,320
I don't want to be kicked again.

37
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:37,741
- You go ahead.
- Jia.

38
00:02:38,340 --> 00:02:39,499
Mom, what are you doing?

39
00:02:39,499 --> 00:02:41,057
Sit down.

40
00:02:43,580 --> 00:02:45,006
Sit down.

41
00:02:52,530 --> 00:02:57,380
Are you angry because I didn't take you to Beijing last time?

42
00:02:57,380 --> 00:02:58,790
No.

43
00:03:03,420 --> 00:03:05,600
I'll tell you the reason now.

44
00:03:07,490 --> 00:03:10,280
I didn't bring you to Beijing last time

45
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:12,700
because I'm incompetent!

46
00:03:15,180 --> 00:03:20,279
Do you think I'm somebody if I run a company and made some money in Beijing?

47
00:03:20,279 --> 00:03:21,939
Let me tell you, Gao Yang.

48
00:03:21,939 --> 00:03:25,320
In Beijing, I'm nobody!

49
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:28,420
There are countless people who are richer and have more connections than me!

50
00:03:28,420 --> 00:03:32,512
At the time, I did want to transfer you to a school here,

51
00:03:33,460 --> 00:03:35,140
but I wasn't able to get it done!

52
00:03:35,140 --> 00:03:38,160
That's why I didn't bring you there. Do you understand now?

53
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:42,060
- Why didn't you tell me earlier?
- Because I didn't want you to know about my incompetence!

54
00:03:44,860 --> 00:03:47,219
Gao Bin is already incompetent.

55
00:03:48,650 --> 00:03:54,640
I wish you can at least feel reassured when you think about me.

56
00:03:58,280 --> 00:04:00,306
My dad is all right.

57
00:04:16,750 --> 00:04:22,260
Son, let's not talk about anything else.

58
00:04:24,770 --> 00:04:27,362
Now, I've got the admission approval from the school for you.

59
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:31,260
Come with me to Beijing and study in a high school here.

60
00:04:31,260 --> 00:04:33,651
After that, we'll go abroad.

61
00:04:33,651 --> 00:04:35,423
Go abroad?

62
00:04:37,740 --> 00:04:41,362
[Episode 27: Razor-Sharp Maternal Love]

63
00:04:54,410 --> 00:04:57,539
Zhan, stop drinking.

64
00:04:57,539 --> 00:05:00,279
Anna is just like that. What she said was just in anger.

65
00:05:00,279 --> 00:05:02,439
Don't take it seriously. She'll be fine in a while.

66
00:05:02,439 --> 00:05:05,479
Exactly. That's how she is.

67
00:05:05,479 --> 00:05:11,240
In terms of our relationship, I understand, love is secondary to her.

68
00:05:11,859 --> 00:05:15,960
Helping each other in our careers is the real thing.

69
00:05:16,850 --> 00:05:19,099
That sounds too much like a utilitarianist.

70
00:05:19,099 --> 00:05:21,580
Anna can be sentimental too.

71
00:05:21,580 --> 00:05:23,203
Yes.

72
00:05:25,260 --> 00:05:29,520
To her, career is the second most important thing.

73
00:05:29,940 --> 00:05:34,600
I'm barely third in line.

74
00:05:36,299 --> 00:05:38,481
What comes first then?

75
00:05:39,020 --> 00:05:40,865
Gao Yang.

76
00:05:43,380 --> 00:05:47,299
That... I really can't tell.

77
00:05:48,090 --> 00:05:52,580
Bin, do you know how I got her to date me?

78
00:05:53,219 --> 00:05:56,940
At the time, a lot of businessmen who came to Beijing from Tieyuan

79
00:05:56,940 --> 00:05:59,520
were trying to pursue Anna.

80
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:03,439
Some of them fancied her money and some fancied her.

81
00:06:03,439 --> 00:06:04,979
I was one of them.

82
00:06:04,979 --> 00:06:07,539
But Anna wouldn't even take one glance at us.

83
00:06:07,539 --> 00:06:10,299
Over the years, she has always been single.

84
00:06:11,090 --> 00:06:17,600
Until last time, I heard she was really anxious because she failed to get admission approval for her son.

85
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:20,340
I just did her a favor.

86
00:06:20,340 --> 00:06:25,020
Unexpectedly, that's how she started to notice me.

87
00:06:28,700 --> 00:06:30,759
We didn't know about that.

88
00:06:31,339 --> 00:06:33,500
Before we got married,

89
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:35,600
she set some rules for me.

90
00:06:36,099 --> 00:06:39,720
She asked me if I will treat Gao Yang nicely.

91
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:44,339
If I can't, I can forget about getting married.

92
00:06:46,020 --> 00:06:47,940
That's what I don't understand.

93
00:06:47,940 --> 00:06:53,219
If Anna loves Gao Yang so much, why did she leave him behind back then?

94
00:06:54,260 --> 00:06:55,861
Bro,

95
00:06:56,900 --> 00:07:00,025
I can tell you've never endured hardship from that comment.

96
00:07:00,900 --> 00:07:05,119
Why didn't Anna bring the child with her when she divorced you?

97
00:07:05,119 --> 00:07:09,259
She was afraid that the child would suffer with her in Beijing.

98
00:07:09,259 --> 00:07:14,800
She would only bring him to Beijing now that she's doing better.

99
00:07:17,820 --> 00:07:19,905
I understand.

100
00:07:19,905 --> 00:07:24,300
You want to take Gao Yang to Beijing for his own good.

101
00:07:24,300 --> 00:07:27,099
But you also have to respect his choice.

102
00:07:27,099 --> 00:07:29,759
After all, he'll be an adult soon.

103
00:07:35,330 --> 00:07:41,619
Bin, there's something else I want to confess to you.

104
00:07:41,619 --> 00:07:43,480
What is it?

105
00:07:47,770 --> 00:07:49,523
Actually,

106
00:07:49,940 --> 00:07:52,937
we're not just going to take Gao Yang to Beijing.

107
00:07:53,419 --> 00:07:56,979
In the future, we're also going to take him abroad.

108
00:07:56,979 --> 00:08:01,900
Anna said, with Gao Yang's grades, he can never pass the college entrance exam.

109
00:08:01,900 --> 00:08:03,899
That's his only choice.

110
00:08:03,899 --> 00:08:05,500
Anna won't let me tell you.

111
00:08:05,500 --> 00:08:07,060
She wants to directly take the kid away.

112
00:08:07,060 --> 00:08:09,260
I think that's...

113
00:08:09,260 --> 00:08:10,820
I don't think what she's doing is right.

114
00:08:10,820 --> 00:08:13,520
It's not right! Of course not!

115
00:08:15,530 --> 00:08:17,174
I'm sorry.

116
00:08:27,820 --> 00:08:29,638
You're here for Gao Yang?

117
00:08:32,860 --> 00:08:34,552
He left.

118
00:08:37,420 --> 00:08:39,245
Xiaowen,

119
00:08:39,245 --> 00:08:40,810
where are you going?

120
00:08:43,020 --> 00:08:45,680
Gao Yang, are you going abroad?

121
00:08:45,680 --> 00:08:47,502
No, I'm not.

122
00:08:47,502 --> 00:08:50,438
Your mom wants to take you abroad. Don't you know that?

123
00:08:50,438 --> 00:08:52,341
I don't know.

124
00:08:53,170 --> 00:08:55,740
Wait, why aren't you worried about it?

125
00:08:55,740 --> 00:08:57,540
What's the point of worrying about it?

126
00:08:57,540 --> 00:09:00,063
We would never see each other again if you go abroad!

127
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,932
You're trying to fool me?

128
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,740
I'm not.

129
00:09:09,740 --> 00:09:13,100
Well, my mom is planning to take me abroad,

130
00:09:13,100 --> 00:09:15,079
but I refused.

131
00:09:16,260 --> 00:09:17,980
What did you say?

132
00:09:17,980 --> 00:09:19,340
Why do you ask?

133
00:09:19,340 --> 00:09:21,059
Let's go.

134
00:09:21,059 --> 00:09:22,279
Where's Gao Bin?

135
00:09:22,279 --> 00:09:24,419
Wait, what exactly did you say?

136
00:09:24,419 --> 00:09:26,059
Don't worry,

137
00:09:26,059 --> 00:09:27,820
I'm not leaving.

138
00:09:30,770 --> 00:09:34,960
But Mom, why didn't you discus such an important matter with me?

139
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:36,959
Have you ever considered my feelings?

140
00:09:36,959 --> 00:09:38,180
I'm your mom.

141
00:09:38,180 --> 00:09:40,759
I'm only concerned about your future. I don't have to consider your feelings!

142
00:09:40,759 --> 00:09:43,220
I don't want the future you planned for me. I don't want to leave.

143
00:09:45,620 --> 00:09:48,479
Gao Yang, you're only seventeen.

144
00:09:48,479 --> 00:09:50,740
You have no idea what you're talking about.

145
00:09:50,740 --> 00:09:52,740
Gao Bin doesn't care either.

146
00:09:52,740 --> 00:09:55,360
Sure, you have a few cronies in Tieyuan

147
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:56,900
and you're pretty happy with your life here.

148
00:09:56,900 --> 00:09:59,360
But let me tell you, everyone must grow up someday.

149
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:01,419
Those cronies of yours can't accompany you for the rest of your life!

150
00:10:01,519 --> 00:10:03,299
- Who said they can't?
- I did!

151
00:10:03,299 --> 00:10:07,640
Gao Yang, I don't care if you hate me. I'll tell the ugly truth up front.

152
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:12,079
In this world, the only person who will be good to you selflessly is me.

153
00:10:14,380 --> 00:10:19,579
Why did I struggle in Beijing for so many years? I did that because of you.

154
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,700
You can go ask around.

155
00:10:21,700 --> 00:10:25,574
Throughout the entire Tieyuan, which child would have this opportunity like you?

156
00:10:27,410 --> 00:10:29,599
To get an opportunity like that,

157
00:10:33,220 --> 00:10:40,800
I've sacrificed many years of my time to be with you.

158
00:10:46,900 --> 00:10:48,365
Mom,

159
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:54,000
I had no idea how much you suffered in Beijing.

160
00:10:56,059 --> 00:11:01,440
I thought I'm not important to you at all.

161
00:11:04,740 --> 00:11:06,879
Now you know.

162
00:11:06,879 --> 00:11:08,637
Come with me.

163
00:11:14,399 --> 00:11:19,000
Mom, thank you.

164
00:11:27,140 --> 00:11:29,120
But I can't go with you.

165
00:11:34,519 --> 00:11:39,299
I know you're worried about your dad.

166
00:11:40,539 --> 00:11:42,045
He'll be fine.

167
00:11:42,860 --> 00:11:45,819
I'll give him some money for retirement.

168
00:11:45,819 --> 00:11:47,639
He won't suffer.

169
00:11:47,639 --> 00:11:49,625
It's not just because of Gao Bin.

170
00:11:53,340 --> 00:11:57,020
Mom, you want to be nice to me.

171
00:11:57,020 --> 00:11:59,047
I want to be nice to someone else too.

172
00:11:59,579 --> 00:12:01,844
I already promised Xiaowen.

173
00:12:01,844 --> 00:12:03,953
Ye Xiaowen?

174
00:12:03,953 --> 00:12:05,328
Yes.

175
00:12:07,290 --> 00:12:09,256
He is an orphan.

176
00:12:10,380 --> 00:12:14,739
But now, he's my brother.

177
00:12:14,739 --> 00:12:16,615
He's family to me.

178
00:12:19,570 --> 00:12:22,100
You see, I have you and Gao Bin.

179
00:12:25,380 --> 00:12:27,339
But I'm the only one he has.

180
00:12:31,650 --> 00:12:36,819
I... used to only think about myself.

181
00:12:37,260 --> 00:12:38,849
It was Xiaowen

182
00:12:40,810 --> 00:12:43,179
who taught me how to be grateful.

183
00:12:46,650 --> 00:12:50,760
Mom, I'll be filial to you in the future.

184
00:12:52,340 --> 00:12:54,359
But I can't go with you.

185
00:13:03,220 --> 00:13:05,107
Mom, I'm sorry.

186
00:13:32,530 --> 00:13:34,189
What are you doing?

187
00:13:38,740 --> 00:13:40,760
Gao Yang told me everything.

188
00:13:40,760 --> 00:13:44,280
I came to have a few words with you.

189
00:13:44,280 --> 00:13:46,739
We're leaving after.

190
00:13:46,739 --> 00:13:48,999
He won't leave with me.

191
00:13:48,999 --> 00:13:50,921
Are you happy now?

192
00:13:53,740 --> 00:13:55,379
Anna,

193
00:13:56,710 --> 00:13:58,620
I don't mean to scold you.

194
00:13:58,620 --> 00:14:02,020
But you've always been like this.

195
00:14:02,020 --> 00:14:03,699
You are more bark than bite.

196
00:14:03,699 --> 00:14:06,959
You care so much about Gao Yang. Why didn't you tell him?

197
00:14:06,959 --> 00:14:09,244
He misunderstood you for so many years.

198
00:14:10,140 --> 00:14:11,980
Zhan Chonghai is such a big mouth.

199
00:14:11,980 --> 00:14:14,359
Don't blame Zhan.

200
00:14:14,359 --> 00:14:16,559
Zhan's a nice guy.

201
00:14:19,770 --> 00:14:21,100
I must give you a piece of advice.

202
00:14:21,100 --> 00:14:24,180
After you get married, be nice to him and talk nicely.

203
00:14:24,180 --> 00:14:25,260
There's more.

204
00:14:25,260 --> 00:14:28,900
For children, what they need is love and companionship.

205
00:14:28,900 --> 00:14:33,279
They don't need money. Their future...
- Shut up!

206
00:14:33,279 --> 00:14:35,560
You have no idea what the outside world is like!

207
00:14:35,560 --> 00:14:38,380
Why are you doing this again?

208
00:14:40,500 --> 00:14:44,020
Gao Bin, what makes you think you can lecture me?

209
00:14:44,020 --> 00:14:48,059
What the child needs is real help.

210
00:14:48,059 --> 00:14:49,299
Not those empty promises.

211
00:14:49,299 --> 00:14:53,099
- I'm not lecturing you. I just want to...
- Move! I'm getting married.

212
00:14:58,100 --> 00:15:00,440
"A leopard cannot

213
00:15:01,659 --> 00:15:03,940
change its spots."

214
00:15:04,659 --> 00:15:08,939
Distinguished Guests, Ladies and Gentlemen,

215
00:15:08,939 --> 00:15:11,380
today is Ms. Anna

216
00:15:11,380 --> 00:15:15,140
and Mr. Zhan Chonghai's wedding ceremony.

217
00:15:15,140 --> 00:15:18,819
They once lingered at the door of happiness.

218
00:15:18,819 --> 00:15:24,240
While they were lingering, they met each other

219
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:27,620
and opened the door of happiness together.

220
00:15:27,620 --> 00:15:31,860
Friends and Family, please congratulate them with a round of applause!

221
00:15:31,860 --> 00:15:34,520
Bravo! Bravo!

222
00:15:36,450 --> 00:15:38,900
Let's wish them a harmonious union forever.

223
00:15:38,900 --> 00:15:42,139
May they grow old together and love each other forever

224
00:15:42,139 --> 00:15:44,639
in happy matrimony!

225
00:15:44,639 --> 00:15:46,919
Bravo! Bravo!

226
00:16:03,860 --> 00:16:07,879
What's wrong? Are you still upset to see my mom marry someone else?

227
00:16:07,879 --> 00:16:08,900
Why should I be upset?

228
00:16:08,900 --> 00:16:13,840
I just think it's our loss that we gave them the red envelope and didn't get to eat anything.

229
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:14,860
Look at you.

230
00:16:14,860 --> 00:16:18,139
Let's go get some dumplings.

231
00:16:18,139 --> 00:16:20,625
- With chives and egg filling?
- Let's go!

232
00:16:23,530 --> 00:16:26,539
Sir, two more orders of dumplings, please!

233
00:16:27,860 --> 00:16:31,020
Mr. Gao, I can't eat anymore.

234
00:16:31,860 --> 00:16:34,620
Xiaowen, you should eat more.

235
00:16:34,620 --> 00:16:37,779
What if Gao Yang changes his mind and wants to go abroad again?

236
00:16:37,779 --> 00:16:40,479
Maybe this is our farewell dinner.

237
00:16:40,479 --> 00:16:44,000
They don't have such delicious dumplings overseas.

238
00:16:44,740 --> 00:16:46,200
What are you talking about?

239
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:48,179
I mean it when I said I'm not leaving.

240
00:16:48,179 --> 00:16:50,241
You're really not leaving?

241
00:16:50,241 --> 00:16:53,299
That's a foreign country. There's no college entrance exam there.

242
00:16:53,299 --> 00:16:57,719
Jin told me our fundamental education is the best in the world.

243
00:16:57,719 --> 00:17:01,459
With your physics, math, and chemistry scores, you'll be the class representative there.

244
00:17:01,459 --> 00:17:03,419
Don't push it.

245
00:17:03,419 --> 00:17:05,660
I'm not staying here because of you.

246
00:17:08,580 --> 00:17:11,299
Oh, I have to thank Xiaowen for that.

247
00:17:11,299 --> 00:17:14,260
I don't have to die alone anymore.

248
00:17:16,319 --> 00:17:20,880
My mom said if I go with her, she'll give you some money.

249
00:17:22,980 --> 00:17:24,359
What?

250
00:17:24,359 --> 00:17:27,140
Who is she trying to look down?

251
00:17:27,140 --> 00:17:29,600
I am an able man. Would I need her to support me?

252
00:17:29,600 --> 00:17:32,019
She's gone too far I'm telling you!

253
00:17:32,599 --> 00:17:33,940
How much?

254
00:17:33,940 --> 00:17:35,499
Enough for the rest of your life.

255
00:17:35,499 --> 00:17:37,580
Deal. Leave!

256
00:17:44,079 --> 00:17:45,294
Come on.

257
00:17:45,294 --> 00:17:46,820
Let's substitute soda for wine.

258
00:17:46,820 --> 00:17:48,420
Cheers.

259
00:17:54,519 --> 00:17:56,960
Stop pretending. Look at how much you want to drink.

260
00:17:56,960 --> 00:17:58,920
Sir, a bottle of beer, please.

261
00:17:58,920 --> 00:18:03,019
Don't, don't. I... I quit.

262
00:18:03,019 --> 00:18:04,698
Just drink a little.

263
00:18:05,240 --> 00:18:07,620
Well, just one bottle then.

264
00:18:07,620 --> 00:18:08,939
Just one bottle.

265
00:18:08,939 --> 00:18:10,739
Just one bottle, okay?

266
00:18:10,739 --> 00:18:13,380
Sir, a bottle of beer, please!

267
00:18:17,810 --> 00:18:20,979
It's been hard for your mom.

268
00:18:22,620 --> 00:18:26,040
She's been single for so long,

269
00:18:28,410 --> 00:18:30,700
just like me.

270
00:18:31,580 --> 00:18:35,959
Although she makes a lot of money,

271
00:18:35,959 --> 00:18:38,499
she doesn't know

272
00:18:39,459 --> 00:18:42,219
what she's missing.

273
00:18:42,219 --> 00:18:50,800
She missed the experience of growing up with you.

274
00:18:52,380 --> 00:18:54,940
Don't drink too much next time.

275
00:18:54,940 --> 00:18:56,800
Although

276
00:18:57,459 --> 00:19:04,018
you're pretty annoying, it's... worth it.

277
00:19:05,589 --> 00:19:07,449
It's worth it.

278
00:19:10,340 --> 00:19:12,432
Check, please!

279
00:19:12,432 --> 00:19:14,100
Go get the check.

280
00:19:14,100 --> 00:19:16,340
We'll go pay the check.

281
00:19:48,300 --> 00:19:49,580
Why are you sighing?

282
00:19:49,580 --> 00:19:54,599
Why do people become more alike as they spend more time together?

283
00:19:54,599 --> 00:19:56,599
Are we alike?

284
00:19:56,599 --> 00:19:58,820
I'm talking about Gao Bin and I.

285
00:20:00,060 --> 00:20:05,600
Look at my mom, she's so eager to excel that Beijing can no longer contain her ambitions.

286
00:20:05,600 --> 00:20:07,300
Why would she have a son like me?

287
00:20:07,300 --> 00:20:11,959
If you don't go abroad, it might be hard for you to see her again.

288
00:20:13,540 --> 00:20:16,259
It's not like I won't see her ever again.

289
00:20:20,540 --> 00:20:23,069
But you're the person she cares about the most.

290
00:20:24,730 --> 00:20:28,880
In the past, I thought all she cared about was money.

291
00:20:28,880 --> 00:20:30,879
Now I realize,

292
00:20:32,250 --> 00:20:35,947
no matter where she is, she's still my mother.

293
00:20:42,650 --> 00:20:47,979
If you go abroad, there will be more opportunities and choices for you.

294
00:20:47,979 --> 00:20:49,695
Have you thought it through?

295
00:20:50,690 --> 00:20:53,160
My mom said the same thing.

296
00:20:53,160 --> 00:20:56,599
She said I'm still young and I don't know anything.

297
00:20:57,490 --> 00:21:00,899
She said I don't know what's the most important thing in life.

298
00:21:00,899 --> 00:21:03,459
It's true that you don't know anything.

299
00:21:04,210 --> 00:21:07,440
So what if I don't know? I'm very happy now.

300
00:21:07,440 --> 00:21:09,920
You are happy now.

301
00:21:09,920 --> 00:21:11,951
But what about the future?

302
00:21:12,790 --> 00:21:14,587
I'll think about that later.

303
00:21:15,860 --> 00:21:18,300
Anyway, I'm your elder brother now.

304
00:21:18,300 --> 00:21:22,543
You want to be my elder brother? Maybe in the next life.

305
00:21:24,780 --> 00:21:28,732
There isn't a next life. This is our only life.

306
00:21:32,810 --> 00:21:36,379
It's not easy to be an elder brother. Why don't I be your elder brother instead?

307
00:21:36,379 --> 00:21:38,324
No way.

308
00:21:38,324 --> 00:21:41,919
Although I'm not perfect now, I will try my best.

309
00:21:41,919 --> 00:21:44,100
Let me watch over you in the future.

310
00:21:44,100 --> 00:21:48,240
Are you sure you can watch over me? I don't think you can.

311
00:21:48,240 --> 00:21:50,280
Why can't I?

312
00:21:50,280 --> 00:21:52,540
You can't run as fast as me.

313
00:21:57,182 --> 00:22:00,362
[Bride]

314
00:22:02,410 --> 00:22:04,344
When are we going back?

315
00:22:05,930 --> 00:22:08,369
You should go back first.

316
00:22:08,369 --> 00:22:10,587
I want to stay for a few more days.

317
00:22:14,100 --> 00:22:15,653
Might as well.

318
00:22:16,410 --> 00:22:22,400
You can spend more time with Gao Yang. It's not easy to see him again in the future.

319
00:22:27,730 --> 00:22:30,104
Is there anything else you need me to do?

320
00:22:34,340 --> 00:22:36,540
This is my own business.

321
00:22:40,820 --> 00:22:44,719
You can go now. Tell my secretary to come in.

322
00:22:58,860 --> 00:23:01,279
Ms. An, you want to see me?

323
00:23:03,730 --> 00:23:07,699
Do a background check on Ye Xiaowen, as detailed as possible.

324
00:23:07,699 --> 00:23:09,127
Okay.

325
00:23:11,642 --> 00:23:13,286
[Canteen]

326
00:23:13,286 --> 00:23:17,048
At the time, my mom wanted to give Gao Bin some money.

327
00:23:17,048 --> 00:23:20,519
My mom would do anything to get custody of me.

328
00:23:20,519 --> 00:23:24,600
And my mom's new husband treated me with a lot of respect too.

329
00:23:24,600 --> 00:23:27,119
He gave me a present the first time we met.

330
00:23:30,580 --> 00:23:34,499
I'm talking to you all. Did you hear me?

331
00:23:34,499 --> 00:23:38,000
Meng, why doesn't that guy love that girl?

332
00:23:38,000 --> 00:23:39,100
He's conflicted.

333
00:23:39,100 --> 00:23:42,300
Xiaowen, eat this. This is delicious.

334
00:23:46,820 --> 00:23:51,639
Are you asleep? Hey, I'm talking to you guys!

335
00:23:51,639 --> 00:23:55,819
Dude, you've been on and on about that for days. Can you leave us alone?

336
00:23:55,819 --> 00:23:57,900
This is an important event of my life, brothers!

337
00:23:57,900 --> 00:24:02,539
Gao Yang, just leave or stay as you wish. You're such a nag.

338
00:24:06,410 --> 00:24:09,399
I thought you guys would be reluctant to part with me!

339
00:24:09,399 --> 00:24:14,660
Yeah, right. Ever since the first time, you keep changing your mind between staying and leaving. How many times have I cried?

340
00:24:14,660 --> 00:24:17,259
I have no more tears for you.

341
00:24:17,259 --> 00:24:20,079
Let's go. Just ignore him.

342
00:24:20,079 --> 00:24:21,359
Xiaowen, go tell them.

343
00:24:21,359 --> 00:24:23,680
So annoying.

344
00:24:27,730 --> 00:24:30,580
You're a Senior now. Concentrate on your studies.

345
00:24:32,340 --> 00:24:34,239
The fickleness of the world.

346
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:42,859
The scores are out from the last monthly exam. Come get your exams when I call your name.

347
00:24:42,859 --> 00:24:44,423
Zhao Jiabao,

348
00:24:45,900 --> 00:24:50,679
even if you're taking the entrance exam for art colleges, you still have to keep up with the literacy classes, right?

349
00:24:50,679 --> 00:24:54,100
Plus, look at your handwriting. It looks like chicken scratch. Work harder, okay?

350
00:24:54,100 --> 00:24:55,730
Okay.

351
00:24:55,730 --> 00:24:57,792
Jin Beibei.

352
00:24:57,792 --> 00:25:01,079
That's right. That's more like the principal's daughter!

353
00:25:02,170 --> 00:25:03,860
Well, of course.

354
00:25:03,860 --> 00:25:06,540
Look at the principal's crazy daughter.

355
00:25:06,540 --> 00:25:08,189
Gao Yang.

356
00:25:11,450 --> 00:25:14,279
Come on, I'm ready. Compliment me.

357
00:25:14,279 --> 00:25:17,359
I was going to compliment you, but I don't want to now. Keep up the good work.

358
00:25:18,300 --> 00:25:20,246
Congratulations.

359
00:25:21,250 --> 00:25:23,114
What's your score?

360
00:25:24,400 --> 00:25:26,023
Zeng Zhi,

361
00:25:27,540 --> 00:25:30,479
I've improved. What do you think?

362
00:25:30,479 --> 00:25:32,203
Mi Jia.

363
00:25:34,180 --> 00:25:36,361
Indeed,

364
00:25:36,361 --> 00:25:39,479
you're still quite far from a college admission.

365
00:25:39,479 --> 00:25:40,759
I'm working on it.

366
00:25:40,759 --> 00:25:41,860
Mi Jia.

367
00:25:41,860 --> 00:25:43,179
I'm still waiting.

368
00:25:43,179 --> 00:25:44,259
Don't worry.

369
00:25:44,259 --> 00:25:49,280
You can run so fast. Why don't you try to catch up? Work harder, okay?

370
00:25:53,620 --> 00:25:54,979
Here we go.

371
00:25:54,979 --> 00:25:56,979
There're shrimps too? What are we celebrating?

372
00:25:56,979 --> 00:25:59,380
Gao Yang improved on this exam.

373
00:26:00,930 --> 00:26:04,439
Good job. There are going to be two college students in our house.

374
00:26:04,439 --> 00:26:05,699
Three.

375
00:26:05,699 --> 00:26:09,960
I'm about to lose my status as the most highly educated in the family. But I'm happy about that.

376
00:26:09,960 --> 00:26:11,939
Here's the last dish.

377
00:26:11,939 --> 00:26:13,765
Let's begin.

378
00:26:16,020 --> 00:26:17,620
Beibei is here to bum a meal again.

379
00:26:17,620 --> 00:26:18,860
I'll go get it.

380
00:26:18,860 --> 00:26:21,171
She learned to knock now.

381
00:26:32,490 --> 00:26:33,459
Anna?

382
00:26:33,459 --> 00:26:36,439
Mom, why are you here? I thought you left.

383
00:26:37,140 --> 00:26:39,582
You can't wait for me to leave, right?

384
00:26:39,582 --> 00:26:43,419
Gao Yang, I'm leaving tonight. I have a few words for you.

385
00:26:43,419 --> 00:26:46,346
Well, sit down and talk then. You can dine with us.

386
00:26:47,380 --> 00:26:50,620
No, let's talk downstairs.

387
00:26:53,340 --> 00:26:56,280
Wait for me. Don't touch the food.

388
00:26:57,860 --> 00:27:01,479
It's cold outside. Bring your jacket.

389
00:27:13,140 --> 00:27:15,739
Mom, what is it? Why can't you say it in the house?

390
00:27:15,739 --> 00:27:17,318
Get in the car.

391
00:27:43,580 --> 00:27:45,389
Gao Yang...

392
00:27:48,820 --> 00:27:51,780
I've been busy making money over the years.

393
00:27:52,650 --> 00:27:55,168
I haven't communicated enough with you either.

394
00:27:55,930 --> 00:28:00,679
I don't know much about your life.

395
00:28:00,679 --> 00:28:05,299
You don't know much about my situation either.

396
00:28:05,970 --> 00:28:07,534
Mom,

397
00:28:10,340 --> 00:28:13,180
I know you want the best for me.

398
00:28:13,180 --> 00:28:15,002
Enough.

399
00:28:17,620 --> 00:28:20,079
Are you sure you're not leaving?

400
00:28:24,510 --> 00:28:28,699
Mom, I am reluctant to part with you too,

401
00:28:31,540 --> 00:28:35,540
but I really can't leave Tieyuan.

402
00:28:37,820 --> 00:28:42,779
You're a grown-up now and you have your own ideas, right?

403
00:28:45,140 --> 00:28:49,200
It's because Xiaowen is a special case.

404
00:28:51,580 --> 00:28:56,880
Don't worry, we'll work hard to get into a college together.

405
00:28:56,880 --> 00:28:58,900
Our future will surely be fine.

406
00:28:58,900 --> 00:29:02,979
Ye Xiaowen is an orphan and you want to help him, right?

407
00:29:05,300 --> 00:29:07,310
Do you have the ability to do so?

408
00:29:09,970 --> 00:29:11,577
What do you mean?

409
00:29:21,060 --> 00:29:22,620
Who are you calling?

410
00:29:22,620 --> 00:29:24,417
Listen.

411
00:29:25,400 --> 00:29:26,620
Hello?

412
00:29:26,620 --> 00:29:28,160
Hello, is this the Sunshine Orphanage?

413
00:29:28,160 --> 00:29:30,599
Hello. You are...?

414
00:29:30,599 --> 00:29:33,100
I'm Anna, the owner of Milana Corp.

415
00:29:33,100 --> 00:29:35,219
My secretary came to see you before.

416
00:29:35,219 --> 00:29:39,740
Oh, Ms. An. Thank you for the kind donations your secretary made on your behalf.

417
00:29:39,740 --> 00:29:44,340
You're welcome. I will ask him to donate another batch over in a while.

418
00:29:44,340 --> 00:29:47,419
That's all right. We appreciate your kindness.

419
00:29:47,419 --> 00:29:49,899
Why?

420
00:29:49,899 --> 00:29:54,200
To be honest with you, our orphanage is about to move soon.

421
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:56,419
Is the orphanage having trouble?

422
00:29:56,419 --> 00:29:58,019
I'm still trying to work it out.

423
00:29:58,019 --> 00:30:02,264
They are increasing the rent and they want us to pay 5 years of rent at once.

424
00:30:02,319 --> 00:30:04,800
That's too much pressure for us.

425
00:30:04,800 --> 00:30:07,839
We still owe a debt out there.

426
00:30:07,839 --> 00:30:11,820
How much money do you need? Do you want my help with that?

427
00:30:11,820 --> 00:30:13,739
No, thank you. It's too much.

428
00:30:13,739 --> 00:30:15,900
We need a few hundred thousand.

429
00:30:15,900 --> 00:30:18,579
What about the children at the orphanage?

430
00:30:18,579 --> 00:30:20,860
I'll find a way to keep the orphanage.

431
00:30:20,860 --> 00:30:23,659
Otherwise, these kids will be homeless.

432
00:30:23,659 --> 00:30:26,259
All right, I see. Please take care.

433
00:30:26,259 --> 00:30:27,519
Okay, thank you.

434
00:30:27,519 --> 00:30:29,073
Bye.

435
00:30:31,620 --> 00:30:33,319
What are you doing?

436
00:30:33,319 --> 00:30:34,860
Xiaowen doesn't know about it yet.

437
00:30:34,860 --> 00:30:36,753
Shut the door.

438
00:30:38,970 --> 00:30:41,320
Do you want to tell him about that?

439
00:30:41,320 --> 00:30:43,540
If you tell him, can you solve the problem?

440
00:30:43,540 --> 00:30:46,179
We can raise money, ask for donations.

441
00:30:46,179 --> 00:30:47,140
You?

442
00:30:47,140 --> 00:30:49,646
How much money can you raise?

443
00:30:53,620 --> 00:30:55,571
Well, what should we do then?

444
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:59,659
I can help him.

445
00:30:59,659 --> 00:31:03,399
But I would only help him on one condition.

446
00:31:03,979 --> 00:31:05,588
What condition?

447
00:31:11,100 --> 00:31:13,980
Take off your sportswear first.

448
00:31:13,980 --> 00:31:15,425
It looks so annoying.

449
00:31:41,780 --> 00:31:44,300
Seems like Anna is really leaving this time.

450
00:31:44,300 --> 00:31:47,039
Their conversation just never ends.

451
00:31:48,077 --> 00:31:50,019
Maybe we shouldn't wait anymore. Let's eat without him.

452
00:31:50,019 --> 00:31:53,599
Let's wait a bit longer. They'll finish soon. Let's wait for Gao Yang.

453
00:31:53,599 --> 00:31:55,074
Sure.

454
00:32:01,300 --> 00:32:03,435
Your stomach is pretty honest.

455
00:32:03,440 --> 00:32:05,759
Wait a minute. I'll go get Gao Yang.

456
00:32:06,419 --> 00:32:08,289
I'll go.

457
00:32:08,739 --> 00:32:10,940
You're afraid I'll argue with Anna?

458
00:32:10,940 --> 00:32:12,499
She's leaving soon.

459
00:32:12,499 --> 00:32:14,659
Leave her a good impression.

460
00:32:15,310 --> 00:32:16,699
You're right. Go on.

461
00:32:16,699 --> 00:32:18,209
Okay.

462
00:32:36,802 --> 00:32:38,935
[Tieyuan No. 3 High School
Sports Games]

463
00:33:16,710 --> 00:33:22,730
♫ I know the direction of dawn ♫

464
00:33:22,730 --> 00:33:29,895
♫  It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine  ♫

465
00:33:29,895 --> 00:33:36,085
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

466
00:33:36,085 --> 00:33:42,025
♫  Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams in my heart  ♫

467
00:33:42,025 --> 00:33:48,477
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

468
00:33:48,477 --> 00:33:54,317
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

469
00:33:54,317 --> 00:33:58,230
♫  To chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

470
00:33:58,230 --> 00:34:01,652
♫  Let's set sail on your dreams  ♫

471
00:34:01,652 --> 00:34:04,947
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

472
00:34:04,947 --> 00:34:11,607
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, I'll be by your side  ♫

473
00:34:11,607 --> 00:34:14,918
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

474
00:34:14,918 --> 00:34:19,130
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

475
00:34:19,130 --> 00:34:22,950
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

476
00:34:22,950 --> 00:34:30,810
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫
